Managing an Application with the Web Console
Go to console. login
Home-->projecs-->create project-->give name
import yaml-->add another content
choose container image
provide image name from external registry as "quay.io/redhattraining/php-hello-dockerfile" and create
Go to workloads-->choose pods , deployment configs,secrets,configmaps etc
click on workloads-->pods-->logs
Go to workloads-->Replication set etc
Go to Networking-->servicesm routes
Go to workloads--> choose pods and -->choose podname -->actions -> delete pod
similarly delete deployment,replication,routes etc
Finally delete project
